videos.description: Tyus Battle knocks down a corner 3-pointer for the Orange to tie Pitt at 15.
videos.headline: Battle ties it with 3 for Cuse

videos.description: Marcus Carr hits a contested 3-pointer to end the half which cuts Pitt's deficit to 2.
videos.headline: Pitt's Carr beats buzzer with 3

videos.description: Oshae Brissett swats away a shot from Terrell Brown, leading to a layup for Tyus Battle.
videos.headline: Brissett rejects Brown at the rim for Cuse

videos.description: Marcus Carr gets knocked down as he fires up a jump shot from the corner to convert the and-1 for the Panthers.
videos.headline: Carr hits and-1 jumper falling down

videos.description: Terrell Brown finds space under the net and forces a Cuse timeout with a wide-open dunk.
videos.headline: Brown jams open dunk for Pitt
